  "detailed_description": "<i> <strong> Velvet Clouds </strong> </i> - a story-driven game with elements of psychological horror and metroidvania. Explore locations, pick up items and destroy various enemies, and immerse yourself in an unusual story, interacting with the playable characters.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Background: </h2>One day, video game developer James decides to create a new project. Development went on without problems and errors, but one day he began to notice that the game began to work differently, not the way it used to: lags that never happened, inexplicably strange behavior of objects, problems with sound. <i> Unravel the mystery of James's broken project, which could be the last in his career. </i>",
